00:03:34.067 --> 00:03:37.434
Michelle Obama wore this dress
to the Inauguration, okay?

00:03:37.434 --> 00:03:39.567
Boom, suddenly,
it sold out, all right?

00:03:39.567 --> 00:03:40.901
Collins-Sussman:
Or Michael Jordan

00:03:40.901 --> 00:03:42.400
wears Nike shoes, right?

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:43.901
Everyone wants to buy Nikes

00:03:43.901 --> 00:03:45.734
'cause they love Jordan
or basketball.

00:03:45.734 --> 00:03:47.167
What's really going on here?

00:03:47.167 --> 00:03:49.167
Like, do you actually believe
that if you buy Air Jordans,

00:03:49.167 --> 00:03:51.234
you're gonna be
