how to protect your project

00:45:03.834 --> 00:45:04.901
from poisonous people.

00:45:04.901 --> 00:45:06.901
So there's a little plug
for that.

00:45:06.901 --> 00:45:08.400
We gave it here
last year, actually.

00:45:08.400 --> 00:45:10.234
Collins-Sussman: That's actually
probably the best prescription

00:45:10.234 --> 00:45:11.601
we have is that talk.

00:45:11.601 --> 00:45:13.400
It's just how to deal
with difficult people in general

00:45:13.400 --> 00:45:14.400
on your project.

