And maybe your company has set
up a certain kind of environment

00:45:42.234 --> 00:45:43.901
at a certain stage in time

00:45:43.901 --> 00:45:47.734
that this kind of way of dealing
with things works.

00:45:47.734 --> 00:45:50.067
