00:46:17.567 --> 00:46:20.067
because you go back
and do these things,

00:46:20.067 --> 00:46:21.901
and you're gonna get
in a lot of trouble

00:46:21.901 --> 00:46:23.067
in a certain environment.

00:46:23.067 --> 00:46:26.067
Secondly,
the no-ego thing is great.

00:46:26.067 --> 00:46:29.067
We'll just send everyone off
to a Zen center for a year.

00:46:29.067 --> 00:46:31.067
[laughter]
You know?

00:46:31.067 --> 00:46:33.901
People have egos.
I'm a psychologist for 30 years.

00:46:33.901 --> 00:46:35.734
I deal with people,
and that's real.

00:46:35.734 --> 00:46:37.734
That's an ego thing.

00:46:37.734 --> 00:46:40.901
Thirdly, there's plenty of
evidence that there are geniuses

00:46:40.901 --> 00:46:42.901
in the world.

00:46:42.901 --> 00:46:45.400
I think that's obvious.

00:46:45.400 --> 00:46:48.067
And there's plenty of evidence
that there's a whole range

00:46:48.067 --> 00:46:50.567
of people that are good
at programming.

00:46:50.567 --> 00:46:52.901
Some people are good. There's
a fair amount of research

00:46:52.901 --> 00:46:54.567
that talks
about the great programmers

00:46:54.567 --> 00:46:57.400
can write 100 times better--

00:46:57.400 --> 00:46:58.901
Fitzpatrick:
I'm gonna stop you there.

00:46:58.901 --> 00:47:01.067
I don't disagree with you on
that--Can you hold on a second?

00:47:01.067 --> 00:47:02.400
I don't disagree with you.

00:47:02.400 --> 00:47:04.400
I'd be glad to talk to you
a little more offline.

00:47:04.400 --> 00:47:05.734
"The genius is a myth" thing

00:47:05.734 --> 00:47:07.400
is definitely a straw man
that we're setting up.

00:47:07.400 --> 00:47:08.701
There are geniuses,

00:47:08.701 --> 00:47:10.167
but the point we're trying
to make precisely

00:47:10.167 --> 00:47:11.501
is that there
are remarkably few.

00:47:11.501 --> 00:47:13.901
There are far fewer
than most people realize.

00:47:13.901 --> 00:47:17.300
And I think our talk
is much more aimed

00:47:17.300 --> 00:47:19.400
at people who are able
to control their project

00:47:19.400 --> 00:47:20.567
or their environment.

00:47:20.567 --> 00:47:22.234
If you're
in a corporate environment

00:47:22.234 --> 00:47:25.234
or something
