has asked me to say

00:47:32.567 --> 00:47:34.734
this is not medical advice.

00:47:34.734 --> 00:47:36.567
[laughter]
And please be careful.

00:47:36.567 --> 00:47:37.901
But please,
we'd love to talk to you more

00:47:37.901 --> 00:47:39.567
about it afterwards in person.
Thanks.

