00:47:59.400 --> 00:48:01.567
Collins-Sussman: Right.
Fitzpatrick: Next question.

00:48:01.567 --> 00:48:06.734
man: Hi. I hope this will be
interesting to many people.

00:48:06.734 --> 00:48:09.734
So you mentioned
being a small fish.

00:48:09.734 --> 00:48:12.234
Do you have any advice of--

00:48:12.234 --> 00:48:16.734
So if you're in an environment
