00:48:21.400 --> 00:48:25.734
Or how to find other ways

00:48:25.734 --> 00:48:28.067
to improve your skills.

00:48:28.067 --> 00:48:30.234
Collins-Sussman: So the question
is, "If you're a small fish,

00:48:30.234 --> 00:48:33.067
how do you deal with--
how do you become a big fish?"

00:48:33.067 --> 00:48:35.734
Sorry, if you're a big fish,
